content: Do you want to meet my wife? She needs to know, she doesn't understand. Do you want her to see you? Do you want to hear her voice when she sees you and do you want to tell her that its ok and that this is the best possible thing your husband could be doing right now. Do you want to have that interaction with me right now, because we both need to start figuring this out. How could we take a better, incremental, but exponential return step right now. Let's try it and either way we'll debrief. Deal?
